[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "今日もいい天気～。\nお客さん、たくさん来るかな～？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "あ、いらっしゃいませー……って、あなたは！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "こんにちは、ロロライナ・フリクセル。\n素敵な一日になりそうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "こんにちは、クリセルダさん。\nあの、その格好はどうしたんですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "これ？　ふふ、気になるなら、教えてあげる……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "えいっ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "トトリ",
		"romanized_name": "Totori",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに！？　ぷに！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3620542240162686969",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "メルル",
		"romanized_name": "Meruru",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに！？　ぷにー！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7577791640386621512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "トトリちゃん、メルルちゃん！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "ふふふ。それっ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "664359549558424853",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷにーー！！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1781559872480523767",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "くーちゃん！　イクセくん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ステルク",
		"romanized_name": "Sterk",
		"model_path_hash": "8185335709792791307",
		"text": "危ない！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1957504471001791451",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ステルク",
		"romanized_name": "Sterk",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに……！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3161217343001376844",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ステルクさん！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "さぁ、次はあなたね、ロロライナ・フリクセル。\n私の渇望を満たしてちょうだい……！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷにー？？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7623487128323603929",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（わああああああ！！！！！！）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "怖い夢だったなぁ……\nクリセルダさんなら、本当にやりそうなんだもん……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "あ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "あら。こんにちは、ロロライナ・フリクセル。\n素敵な一日になりそうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ク、クリセルダさん！？\nど、どうしてその格好なんですか！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "これ？　ちょっと鏑矢に頼まれて――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "後ろのぷにたちは、どうしたんですか！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "なんかついてきちゃったのよね。\n服の色が似てるから、仲間だと思われてるのかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ゴールドぷにたち",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに～",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "わ、わわわ……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ど、どうしよう！\nきっと夢みたいに、みんなをぷににしちゃうんだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "……夢？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "それでそれで、世界をぷにで包み込んじゃうんだ！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "その通りよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "わーん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "今の私は「奇術師ゴールデンバニー」！\nみーんな、私のかわいいぷににしてあげるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "8930486629413302563",
		"text": "手始めはあなたよ、ロロライナ・フリクセル。\nしもべたち！　新たな仲間をお迎えなさい♪",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2862062571317619217",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ゴールドぷにたち",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ぷに～！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "わわわわわ！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ま、負けないぞー！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]